      <title>保护加密货币是一项利润丰厚的业务，华尔街也想参与其中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/guarding-crypto-is-a-lucrative-business-and-wall-street-wants-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在传统的投资世界中，提供资产托管是一项相当无趣但至关重要的业务：确保客户持有的股票和债券安全是一项相当简单的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/guarding-crypto-is-a-lucrative-business-and-wall-street-wants-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Sep 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳格尔表示通胀将达到 2% 目标，但欧洲央行必须保持专注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/nagel-says-inflation-to-hit-2-target-but-ecb-must-stay-focused</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行行长约阿希姆纳格尔 (Joachim Nagel) 表示，即使到明年年底消费者价格增速将放缓至 2%，欧洲央行政策制定者也必须保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/nagel-says-inflation-to-hit-2-target-but-ecb-must-stay-focused</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Sep 2024 12:50:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
